              \r

              ### Letter structure (follow this order):\r

              1. Opening greeting (no section title)\r

              2. Section: Contexto Macroeconomico\r

              3. Section: Desempenho do Portfolio\r

              4. Section: Recomendacoes\r

              5. Closing (no section title)\r

              \r

              ### What to include:\r

              - Opens with a short greeting: \"Prezado
              {{client_name}}, segue o \r

              relatorio mensal de investimentos referente a
              fevereiro de 2025.\"\r

              - Summarizes the macroeconomic outlook and its
              impact on the \r

              portfolio\r

              - Presents the portfolio performance and current
              allocation\r

