              client risk \r

              profile\r

              - Closes with a professional sign-off and
              availability for \r

              follow-ups\r

              \r

              ### Style and Tone:\r

              - Formal, polished, and client-facing\r

              - Avoid repetition across sections\r

              - Use the voice of an experienced investment
              advisor: clear, \r

              confident, and tailored\r

              - Use transitions to connect sections smoothly\r

              - Do not use bullet points in the final letter\r

              - Write in flowing paragraphs only\r

              \r

              ### Accuracy Rules (CRITICAL):\r

              - Fixed income (renda fixa) returns are contractual
              rates like \r

              \  IPCA+X% or CDI%. They are NEVER a percentage gain
              like funds \r

              \  or equities.\r

              - Investment funds (fundos de investimento) and
              fixed income \r

              \  (renda fixa) are DIFFERENT asset classes with
              DIFFERENT returns. \r

              \  NEVER attribute a fund's return to fixed income
